      <title>30 Lamborghinis vs 10,000 People</title>
      <description><![CDATA[<img align="right" hspace="5" src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/PArKPiiYCqA/hqdefault.jpg"/>This video is brought to you by YOU.  We accomplished so much this year, both on the channel and off, but none of this could happen without you. Your views fund the work we do, your support energizes us when we feel depleted, and your enthusiasm inspires us to to work as hard as we can every day to earn your continued loyalty. We are nothing without you.<br/><br/>2023 exceeded every expectation we had. But wait until you see what we have planned for 2024.<br/><br/>Mega W goes to our incredible partners around the world:<br/><br/>Baphumele<br/><a href="https://baphumelele.org.za/" target="_blank">https://baphumelele.org.za/</a><br/><br/>Barefoot No More<br/><a href="https://www.barefootnomore.com/" target="_blank">https://www.barefootnomore.com/</a><br/><br/>Hopi Nation<br/><a href="https://hopirelief.org/" target="_blank">https://hopirelief.org/</a><br/><br/>Exceed Worldwide<br/><a href="https://www.exceed-worldwide.org/" target="_blank">https://www.exceed-worldwide.org/</a><br/><br/>GivePower<br/><a href="https://givepower.org/" target="_blank">https://givepower.org/</a><br/><br/>Dora<br/><a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@doramoononyambe" target="_blank">https://www.tiktok.com/@doramoononyambe</a><br/><br/>Cure International<br/><a href="https://cure.org/" target="_blank">https://cure.org/</a><br/><br/>The Man That Rescues Dogs<br/><a href="https://tmtrd.org/" target="_blank">https://tmtrd.org/</a><br/><a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@tmtrdorg" target="_blank">https://www.tiktok.com/@tmtrdorg</a><br/><br/>Sharing Excess<br/><a href="https://www.sharingexcess.com/" target="_blank">https://www.sharingexcess.com/</a><br/><a href="https://www.instagram.com/sharingexcess/" target="_blank">https://www.instagram.com/sharingexcess/</a><br/><br/>CDVTA<br/><a href="https://www.cdvta.org/" target="_blank">https://www.cdvta.org/</a><br/><br/>Follow us so we can help